er2.scbdd.com/server/interact/150380/', '', 'Cholecalciferol, Vosoritide, Denosumab, Burosumab', 'Entrectinib, Pralsetinib, Dabrafenib, Asciminib, Acalabrutinib, Dacomitinib, Pexidartinib, Pacritinib, Tepotinib, Fedratinib, Avapritinib, More', 1767369485);
