onal information.', 'Synergism', 'Caution is recommended when panobinostat is used in combination with SSRIs or other medicines with SRI properties.', 'Major', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/150418/', '', 'Ephedrine, Bupropion, Phentermine, Orlistat, Lorcaserin, Sibutramine, Diethylpropion, Mazindol', 'Pertuzumab, Olaparib, Oxaliplatin, Rucaparib, Bortezomib, Tisagenlecleucel, Aminolevulinic acid, Omacetaxine mepesuccinate, Altretamine, Tagraxofusp, Pegaspargase, More', 1767369485);
